replies.body:
He's pure utility and not damage.

Sound familiar? {{champion:40}} {{champion:16}} 


These champs will always be good, because utility isn't ever bad. It's always neutral, so those champs will have relatively consistent, high winrates. The only way to nerf them is by nerfing their utility, either straight out, or making the utility have a lower base % and making it scale off AP/AD, to make them feast/famine(like Lulu).
